{"title":"Java 实例 - 查找 List 中的最大最小值","date":"2019-01-10T17:31:26.000Z","link":"post/293","categories":["Java"],"updated":"2019-04-27T12:20:46.594Z","content":"<p>以下实例演示了如何使用 Collections 类的 max() 和 min() 方法来获取List中最大最小值：</p>\n<h3 id=\"例1：\">例1：<a href=\"post/293#例1：\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/*</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> author by w3cschool.cc</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> Main.java</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> java.util.*;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Main</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      List list = Arrays.asList(<span class=\"string\">\"one Two three Four five six one three Four\"</span>.split(<span class=\"string\">\" \"</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">      System.out.println(list);</span><br><span class=\"line\">      System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"最大值: \"</span> + Collections.max(list));</span><br><span class=\"line\">      System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"最小值: \"</span> + Collections.min(list));</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>以上代码运行输出结果为：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[one, Two, three, Four, five, six, one, three, Four]</span><br><span class=\"line\">最大值: three</span><br><span class=\"line\">最小值: Four</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"例2：\">例2：<a href=\"post/293#例2：\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">List&lt;Double&gt; input = new ArrayList&lt;Double&gt;();</span><br><span class=\"line\">input.add(2.3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">input.add(3.3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">input.add(4.3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">input.add(5.3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">input.add(6.3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">input.add(7.3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">input.add(8.3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">input.add(9.3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">input.add(1.3);\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">System.out.println(input);</span><br><span class=\"line\">System.out.println(&quot;最大值: &quot; + Collections.max(input));</span><br><span class=\"line\">System.out.println(&quot;最小值: &quot; + Collections.min(input));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>以上代码运行输出结果为：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[2.3, 3.3, 4.3, 5.3, 6.3, 7.3, 8.3, 9.3, 1.3]</span><br><span class=\"line\">最大值: 9.3</span><br><span class=\"line\">最小值: 1.3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Java StringBuffer insert()方法","link":"post/294"},"next":{"title":"正则表达式——过滤非字母字符","link":"post/292"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/293/"}